---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Origin Direct Group"
  description="Terms and conditions for Origin Direct Group commodity trading services."
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-gray">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-8">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Services</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Origin Direct Group provides B2B commodity sourcing, quality control, documentation, and logistics services. We act as an intermediary between commodity producers in West Africa and India and international buyers.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Quote Requests</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Submitting a quote request through our website does not constitute a binding agreement. All quotes provided are indicative and subject to market conditions, availability, and final confirmation by both parties.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Pricing</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">All prices quoted are subject to change based on market conditions, exchange rates, and commodity availability. Firm pricing is confirmed only upon acceptance of a formal purchase order or contract.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Payment Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Payment terms are agreed upon individually for each transaction and may include Letter of Credit (LC), Telegraphic Transfer (TT), or Cash Against Documents (CAD). Specific terms are outlined in individual contracts.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Quality & Specifications</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Product specifications listed on this website are indicative and represent typical ranges. Exact specifications are confirmed per shipment and documented in the Certificate of Analysis provided with each order.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Shipping & Delivery</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Delivery terms (FOB, CIF, DDP) are agreed per transaction. Transit times listed on this website are estimates and may vary based on shipping schedules, port conditions, and customs processing.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Information provided on this website is for general informational purposes only. While we strive for accuracy, we make no warranties regarding the completeness or accuracy of website content. HS codes, duty rates, and regulatory information should be verified with relevant authorities.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">These terms are governed by the laws of Hong Kong SAR. Any disputes arising from commodity transactions will be resolved according to the terms specified in individual contracts.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">For questions about these terms, please contact us through our <a href="/quote" class="text-brand-700 hover:text-brand-600 underline">contact form</a>.</p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-8">Origin Direct Group<br />Unit 2201, 22/F Chung Kiu Comm. Bldg.<br />47-51 Shan Tung St. Mongkok<br />Hong Kong</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
